title: Martin Dostál
text:
Martin Dostál (born 23 September 1989) is a <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="Bohemians%201905">Bohemians 1905</a>. 
Club career.
He made his <a href="Gambrinus%20liga">Gambrinus liga</a> debut for Slavia against <a href="FC%20Zbrojovka%20Brno">Brno</a> on 25 February 2011.
